        <option name="charting.legend.placement">bottom</option>
        <option name="charting.legend.masterLegend">null</option>
        <option name="charting.seriesColors">[0x293E6A, 0x77BA9B, 0x3B5998, 0x639BF1, 0xB6A754, 0xC9E1C1, 0xFF9900, 0xFF5A09, 0x0F9FB4, 0x1D2F3E]</option>
        <option name="height">350px</option>
      </chart>
    </panel>
  </row>
  <row>
    <panel>
      <html>
        <h2>Multiple Time Range Pickers</h2>
        <p>Add and configure multiple time range pickers on a single dashboard</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Assign each time range picker a unique token value (this will automatically set tokens $token.earliest$ and $token.latest$</li>
          <li>For each panel search, select, (a) a shared time range picker referenced by label/token name, (b) inline explicit time range, or (c) other token values to use for earliest and latest</li>
        </ul>
      </html>
    </panel>
  </row>
</form>